心目中全部黃絲都係咩野都唔知<br />\n的確唔排除有部分係有啲野睇唔清<br />\n但如果真係咁 佢地更加應該提醒而唔係下下屌"},{"pid":"9ac4c5b2741295b5ae56f8835c73be37d24bbb01","tid":2127053,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f269ddc121fbb227c311c8330e673ada9b2a0e3","tid":2127053,"uid":89030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:42:46.000Z","msg":"佢地最鐘意講戴到落棺材<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:16:50.000Z","msg":"呢句都成日聽<br />\n有時為己為人 唔知自己係咪隱形病者<br />\n亦唔知會唔會傳左比啲老人家/長期病患"},{"pid":"e236652d291dbbe3177d956981acee400d9bdf05","tid":2127053,"uid":7818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T10:35:35.000Z","msg":"白兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a437ce75ba6cd7bb74261826d0d9e4b1325972","tid":2127053,"uid":150962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"736f981563edc8cf6d7ace2119a3390cfe030906","tid":2127053,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"佢地好鍾意冷嘲熱諷<br />\n<br />\n例如而家政府借疫情推好多限制人生自由既野<br />\n另外亦借機引入中國醫護<br />\n將來再推健康碼等等<br />\n<br />\n基本上大部分人都知政府係借疫情黎行暴政<br />\n<br />\n但facebook總係人有啲人覺得得佢地先知 鍾意冷嘲熱諷：<br />\n『啲黃絲繼續聽政府話啦』<br />\n(但明明大部分人都唔支持政府呢啲措施)<br />\n<br />\n『啲香港人仲傻下傻下支持禁堂食』<br />\n(但明明大部分人都反對 一開始已經知借疫情重創飲食業 仲串政府係咪同病毒deal好6點後先出黎)<br />\n<br />\n『黃絲繼續鳩戴口罩啦』<br />\n(戴口罩都係保障人同保障自己 大家都知中年或以下死亡率接近0 但最怕係中左傳比年長家人/長期病患)<br />\n<br />\n『個個走去做檢測 爭住將自己資料送中』<br />\n(明明一早有人起左果三間支那公司底 亦都講話準確度低 更唔知佢會唔會直接將資料送中)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:51:15.000Z","msg":"果班熱狗ban橋王 剩係識ban橋 唔俾建議 立於不敗之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為世上無一個完美無缺既建議 任何一個建議都有對邊個好對邊個衰 又或者犧牲少數利益 成全多數利益 針無兩頭利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熱狗只係拎所有建議既壞處黎講黎批評 唔俾任何建議 想唔贏都幾難啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但問佢有咩高見 就被串錦鯉有咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢齋識ban橋 唔識俾建議呀麻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢一俾建議 自然有位入被串啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地就醒啦 長期做批評者 永遠做道德贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52943d51abcc97235446ae9c148fbc612c9a10f","tid":2127053,"uid":131157,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"51466f1dc5f2ad5008a5e53a70665a472156fdee","tid":2127053,"uid":57287,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自以為看透世事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"係丫，全部都係熱狗<br />\n唔認熱狗都係熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc9f1c3dda68de7b2c5ffd81444fd0fa91d5999","tid":2127053,"uid":126977,"like":1,"disli